---
title: Retry & Caching Mechanism
---
flowchart TD
    subgraph RETRY["Retry: Exponential Backoff"]
        direction TB
        R1["📡 API Call"] --> R2{"Success?"}
        R2 -->|Yes| R3["✅ Return Result"]
        R2 -->|No| R4["⏳ Wait delay × 2^attempt<br/>attempt 1: 2s<br/>attempt 2: 4s<br/>attempt 3: 8s"]
        R4 --> R1
        R2 -->|"No (3 attempts)"| R5["❌ Error → Fallback"]
    end

    subgraph CACHE["Caching per-Chunk"]
        direction TB
        C1["Chunk Name:<br/>chunk_001.wav"] --> C2["MD5 Hash:<br/>a1b2c3d4..."]
        C2 --> C3{"Cache file exists?"}
        C3 -->|Yes| C4["✅ Load from JSON<br/>output/transcripts/a1b2c3d4.json"]
        C3 -->|No| C5["🔄 Process chunk"]
        C5 --> C6["💾 Save to JSON"]
        C6 --> C4
    end

    RETRY --> CACHE
